org.ObjectLayout

Interface CtorAndArgsProvider<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the element occupying each array slot.

    public interface CtorAndArgsProvider<T>
    A functional interface for providing a constructor and arguments given a construction context (index, etc.). Used for providing element construction information in StructuredArrays.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      CtorAndArgs<T> getForContext(ConstructionContext<T> context)
      Get a CtorAndArgs instance to be used in constructing a given element index in a StructuredArray
